description:
https://developer.openstack.org/api-ref/compute/#evacuate-server-evacuate-action

In API reference, the followings should be fixed.

* Unnecessary note

* The 'on_shared_storage' parameter
  The max version(2.14 --> 2.13)
    
* The 'evacuate' parameter
  The type(string --> object)
    
* The 'adminPass' parameter
  Remove max version.
    
* response code
  Unncessary response code.
title: api-ref: wrong response code and parameters in servers-action-evacuate.inc
